1. To compile Isaac, type

> make

To clean up the exutables, type

> make clean

2. To get the irrlicht client, first make sure you have all necessary libraries installed. Type

> ./installLibraries

You will be asked for the root password.

Next, get irrlicht, build it, and build the IrrClient. Type

./getIrrlicht

If the build is not successful, execute the steps in the script manually.

3. Test Isaac with irrlicht. Type

> ./TestGameEngine -i data/testconfig.cfg

Press Z to exit the irrlicht client, ctrl+c to kill the server.
